WEBVTT

00:00.805 --> 00:05.820
An offer to read English
at Bristol is fantastic, Rae.

00:05.920 --> 00:07.900
I'm not going.

00:07.959 --> 00:10.959
Move in. Here, with me?

00:10.959 --> 00:13.958
It's never too late to be what
you might have been.

00:13.959 --> 00:15.518
Why would you lie to me?

00:15.519 --> 00:17.838
Finn! Well, what about the party?

00:17.839 --> 00:20.079
I'm not really in the mood.

00:22.639 --> 00:26.038
We are going to have the flat-warming
party. It is back on!

00:26.039 --> 00:27.318
I need you to come with me.

00:27.319 --> 00:28.599
It's a lock-in!

00:30.599 --> 00:32.558
Yeah!

00:32.558 --> 00:33.639
Chloe!

