00:55.519 --> 00:58.879
I think we should do a rota,
so that someone's always here.

00:58.880 --> 01:02.239
I'll go first. Just make sure
I'm back for three.

01:02.239 --> 01:05.958
Got to take Rita to the
park to do a shit.

01:05.959 --> 01:08.238
Me dad's dog.

01:08.239 --> 01:10.878
Well, if you're staying,
I'm staying. Maybe I should stay.

01:10.879 --> 01:13.598
Well, we can't all stay.
What sort of rota's that?

01:13.599 --> 01:16.038
Guys...

01:16.039 --> 01:18.758
It's OK. I'll do it.

01:18.759 --> 01:21.238
You go and get some rest.

01:21.239 --> 01:24.678
What's going on?

01:24.679 --> 01:26.701
What's happened?

01:32.169 --> 02:07.566
